<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ لَبِيدُ بن رَبيعَةَ العَامِريُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الرمل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - إِنَّ تَقْوَى رَبِّنَا خَيْرُ نَفَلْ ... وَبِإذْنِ اللهِ رَيْثِس وَعَجَلْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤٧)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ عَدِيُّ بنُ زِيْدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الرمل)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - فَدَعِ الْبَاطِلَ وَالْحَقْ بالتُّقَى ... فَتُقَى رَبِّكَ رَهْنٌ لِلرَّشَدْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤٨)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الأَعَشَى:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - إذا أَنْتَ لَمْ تَرْحَلْ بِزَادٍ مِنَ التُّقَى ... وَلاقَيْتَ بَعْدَ الْمَوْتِ مَنْ قَدْ تَزَوَّدَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢ - نَدِمْتَ عَلَى أَنْ لا تَكونَ كمِثْلِهِ ... فَتُرْصِدَ لِلْمَوْتِ الّذِي هُوَ أَرْصَدَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤٩)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْن مُقْبلٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - تَقُولُ تَرَبَّحْ يعْمُرُ الْمَالُ أَهْلَهُ ... كبَيْشَةُ وَالتَّقْوَى إلَى اللهِ أَرْبَحُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٨٥٠)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ هُدْبةُ بنُ خَشْرَمٍ الْعُذْرِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>